                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240916-187-victim1581 t18240916-187-viclabel1017"></join>. The prisoner was my <rs id="t18240916-187-deflabel1018" type="occupation">apprentice</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240916-187-defend1579 t18240916-187-deflabel1018"></join>. On the 30th of July, I missed a watch: I saw it safe on the evening of the 28th I am certain, and think that it hung in my bed-room. I did not always wear it. He went out on Thursday evening, the 29th, and did not return at all. I found him at the watch-house on Saturday the 31st.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18240916-187-person1583">
                  WILLIAM 
                  CREED
               <interp inst="t18240916-187-person1583" type="surname" value="CREED"></interp>
