                     <interp inst="t18240916-187-person1583" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a pawn-broker, and live in Gray's-inn-lane. On the 30th of July, between seven and eight o'clock in the morning, the prisoner came to redeem some articles, and pawned a watch for 20 s.; it is worth 30 s. We asked him if it was his own; he said it was.</p>
